text: KADH may refer to: * Ada Municipal Airport (ICAO code KADH) * KJJC (AM), a radio station (1230 AM) licensed to serve Murray, Utah, United States, which held the call sign KADH in 2017 * α-ketoacid dehydrogenase complexes (KADH), which are pyruvate dehydrogenase (PDH), α-ketoglutarate dehydrogenase (KGDH) and branched chain α-keto acid dehydrogenase (BCDH).
title: KADH
